Description: Cortex Linux Security Operations meta-package
 This meta-package installs security monitoring, intrusion detection,
 and compliance tools for Cortex Linux deployments.
 .
 Includes:
  - Audit framework (auditd) with comprehensive logging
  - File integrity monitoring (AIDE, Tripwire)
  - Intrusion detection (Fail2ban, rkhunter, chkrootkit)
  - Antivirus scanning (ClamAV)
  - Security auditing (Lynis)
  - Log analysis (logwatch)
  - System accounting (sysstat, acct)
  - Firewall management (nftables, ufw)
 .
 After installation, run 'cortex secops init' to configure
 security baselines and enable monitoring.
